<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT95">
<l>ēṉṟē ṉaṭimai yiḻintēṉ piṟappiṭumpai</l>
<l>yāṉṟē ṉamarark kamarāmai yāṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>kaṭaṉṉāṭu maṇṇāṭuṅ kaiviṭṭu mēlai</l>
<l>yiṭaṉāṭu kāṇa viṉi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have accepted service [to Him]; I have fallen [away from] the affliction of birth.</l>
<l>I have been filled [with devotion so that] the [other] immortal [gods]</l>
<l rend="indent">do not to get close [to me].</l>
<l>Giving up the borrowed land and the earthly land,</l>
<l>I have become filled [with desire] to now see the land of the place located</l>
<l rend="indent">above [these].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
